- `AMZN`\
- `GOOGL`\
- `MSFT`\
- `UDMY`\
- `NXE`\
- `SPY`\
- `CDR.WA`\
- `EH`\
- `BTC-USD`\
- `ETH-USD`\
\
Current local structure:\
\
- `data/raw/daily/`: roughly 5 years of daily data\
- `data/raw/hourly/`: recent hourly data for short-term momentum\
